data.description: Check out this well-maintained 3 bed/2 bath block home on a cul-de-sac!  Since being purchased in 2019, this home has an updated A/C and Air Handler (2019), new roof (2022), and new windows (2022). The covered parking/man cave was added in 2019 and can be used for a variety of purposes.  You can enter the house through the newly added screened-in lanai, right into the living room. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet and newly renovated master bathroom. The kitchen is equipped with a snack/serving bar, newer appliances and granite countertops! The garage was mostly-enclosed to make a 3rd bedroom, office, playroom, etc. There is a storage room with access through the working garage door with storage about 8 feet deep-perfect for bikes and lawnmower! The covered back porch was just added this year! Conveniently located near I4, and close to shopping, restaurants and medical facilities.
